        {
          "id": "db4335f8c678_12",
          "href": null,
          "name": "6c3f",
          "text": "In 2013 and important UNCTAD report called for an urgent return to small scale higly productive traditional and organic farming practices. ( image middle, image right)",
          "metadata": null,
          "mixtapeMetadata": null,
          "hasDropCap": null,
          "dropCapImage": null,
          "iframe": null,
          "layout": null,
          "markups": [
            {
